# Always Use Bun

This project uses **Bun** as its runtime, package manager, and build tool.

## Package Management

- Use `bun install` instead of `npm install` or `yarn install`
- Use `bun add <package>` instead of `npm install <package>`
- Use `bun remove <package>` instead of `npm uninstall <package>`

## Running Scripts

- Use `bun run <script>` instead of `npm run <script>`
- Use `bun test` instead of `npm test` or `npx vitest`

## Executing Files

- Use `bun run <file>` instead of `node <file>` or `npx tsx <file>`

## Installing Tools

- Use `bunx <tool>` instead of `npx <tool>`
